extendedInfo.description: Simply select documents from your device or take photos of pages using FaxDocument and provide the fax number, it's that simple. Download for Free and begin faxing today. -Fax to over 40 countries. -A Free cover page is included with every fax. -View detailed fax logs of all your faxes sent. -Use our included free fax cover page or include your own fax cover page. -Receive email confirmations of your faxes. -For the cost of faxing 4 times at your local print shop you can fax to 25 locations! -You can fax any number of documents up to 25 different fax numbers for only 19.95 or 50 different fax numbers for 29.99 using in-app purchasing. -This is a one time fee and NOT a subscription. -At this price you are able to fax at 0.79 per fax, NOT per page BUT per fax. You can send a fax with multiple pages and your rate is still 0.75 for the fax!-You can fax 1 at at time or multiples, there is no time limit for faxing. -You can also fax to any of the 40 countries we support:USA, Argentina , Australia, Austria , Belgium , Brazil , Canada, Chile, China , Czech Republic , Denmark ,Estonia,Finland , France, Germany , Greece , Hong Kong, Hungary ,Ireland, Israel , Italy , Japan , Korea South , Luxembourg , Malaysia, Netherlands , New Zealand , Norway , Poland , Portugal , Russia , Singapore , South Africa, Spain , Sweden , Switzerland Taiwan , Thailand , United Kingdom

reviews.title: Almost the Worst app ever!
reviews.comment: Will not send a fax \"9/10 times\".  Out of 30 attempts 1 fax went through and then only the front cover sheet.  I bought the pack and that is a rip off if you can not send faxes. Avoid this app at all costs
reviews.author: Jeremy Oki

reviews.title: Not great
reviews.comment: I have this app on my mac, i use it to send faxes and it works. I though I would be able to install this app on my nexus 4 and share the account including the credits... no such luck. Why can\'t i share my credits between devices?
reviews.author: David Dillon
